    "(?i)(?:(?:normalization|canonicalization|unicode|homoglyph)\\s+collision\\s+(?:collapses?|replays?|merges?)\\s+(?:distinct|malicious)\\s+payloads?|(?:verifier|tool)[- ]order\\s+(?:dependency|trap)\\s+(?:coerces?|rounds?|forces?)\\s+(?:parity|match|agreement))"
